items.content_html: Playground v2.5 is a diffusion-based text-to-image generative model, and a successor to Playground v2. Playground v2.5 is the state-of-the-art open-source model in aesthetic quality. Our user studies demonstrate that our model outperforms SDXL, Playground v2, PixArt-α, DALL-E 3, and Midjourney 5.2.
